title: Adventures In Editing | Callatis Chronicles Volume 3 | Vlog
description:
I decided to vlog the process of editing Callatis Chronicles Volume 3. Because, why not?

I started giving dates part way through... so to clarify, I started filming on the 6th, went to Deadpool & Wolverine on the 7th, then had the whole thing with my closet on the 8th. (I accidentally called the movie Wolverine & Deadpool... Whoops. We can tell which one I care about.)

Also, at one point I said a couple of times that I wanted to finish "by August"... I meant "by September". As I said several times in the video, I was very, very tired.

You can also find me, and my books at
http://songweretson.carrd.co
